{"by":"onionisafruit","id":47774752,"parent":47773812,"text":"The people who will benefit from a cooldown weren’t reviewing updates anyway. Without the cooldown they would just be one more malware victim. If you don’t review code before you update, it just makes sense to wait until others have. Despite what the article says, the only people who benefit from a rush to update are the malware spreaders.","time":1776227999,"type":"comment"}